1
00:00:12,140 --> 00:00:16,570
[Hanzhou City, 2002]

2
00:00:41,810 --> 00:00:42,390
Freeze!

3
00:00:42,390 --> 00:00:43,190
We're police!

4
00:00:53,640 --> 00:00:54,520
You quick runner.

5
00:00:54,520 --> 00:00:55,120
Stay down!

6
00:00:55,430 --> 00:00:56,110
Ease up a little.

7
00:00:56,110 --> 00:00:57,200
I'm on your side.

8
00:00:57,200 --> 00:00:57,670
Behave!

9
00:00:57,670 --> 00:00:58,870
How are you on my side?

10
00:00:59,430 --> 00:01:00,960
Wait, are you new to the force?

11
00:01:00,960 --> 00:01:02,150
My name is Mai Hongchao.

12
00:01:02,150 --> 00:01:03,280
Does anyone know me?

13
00:01:04,040 --> 00:01:06,300
Go ask around about me. I'm Mai Hongchao.

14
00:01:06,950 --> 00:01:08,350
Crazy! What's this about?

15
00:01:08,350 --> 00:01:09,610
You've got good moves.

16
00:01:10,150 --> 00:01:11,080
Release him now.

17
00:01:11,310 --> 00:01:12,150
He's the eldest senior to you.

18
00:01:12,150 --> 00:01:14,150
I already told you I was on your side.

19
00:01:14,400 --> 00:01:15,230
Mind your hands.

20
00:01:15,230 --> 00:01:16,690
Where's this rookie from?

21
00:01:16,920 --> 00:01:17,840
He's really stubborn.

22
00:01:17,840 --> 00:01:19,280
You put on quite a convincing act.

23
00:01:19,280 --> 00:01:20,590
How could he have not arrested you?

24
00:01:20,590 --> 00:01:22,150
I told you to ease up a little

25
00:01:22,150 --> 00:01:22,920
and that I was on your side.

26
00:01:22,920 --> 00:01:24,230
But you wouldn't believe me
and kept pinning me down.

27
00:01:24,230 --> 00:01:25,590
That really strained my back.

28
00:01:25,590 --> 00:01:26,120
He's mad now.

29
00:01:26,120 --> 00:01:26,760
But it's okay.

30
00:01:26,760 --> 00:01:28,430
Mentor's kick was so powerful.

31
00:01:28,430 --> 00:01:30,490
My adrenaline shot through the roof.

32
00:01:30,789 --> 00:01:32,590
That's Mentor's signature move.

33
00:01:32,590 --> 00:01:33,229
Learn from it.

34
00:01:33,229 --> 00:01:35,509
They're talking about me, not you, Mentor.

35
00:01:35,509 --> 00:01:37,310
Mentor, did you recruit this guy?

36
00:01:37,310 --> 00:01:38,820
I said I was on his side,

37
00:01:39,070 --> 00:01:40,070
yet he still held me down.

38
00:01:40,070 --> 00:01:41,280
Look, now my back's hurt.

39
00:01:41,280 --> 00:01:42,410
He caught you wrong?

40
00:01:42,759 --> 00:01:43,759
I hadn't met him until just now.

41
00:01:43,759 --> 00:01:44,960
And he just seized me!

42
00:01:49,200 --> 00:01:51,330
It's okay. At least we caught this one.

43
00:01:54,420 --> 00:01:55,259
Mai,

44
00:01:56,710 --> 00:01:58,950
your real identity aside,

45
00:01:59,400 --> 00:02:01,660
after being friends for such a long time,

46
00:02:01,710 --> 00:02:02,870
can I ask you a favor?

47
00:02:04,120 --> 00:02:04,870
Go ahead.

48
00:02:05,230 --> 00:02:06,430
It's about my father.

49
00:02:07,710 --> 00:02:09,750
He's dying. Can I pay a visit to him?

50
00:02:15,240 --> 00:02:16,310
Well...

51
00:02:17,430 --> 00:02:19,490
You need to follow normal procedure.

52
00:02:20,190 --> 00:02:21,360
But exceptional circumstances

53
00:02:21,360 --> 00:02:23,430
call for exceptional measures.

54
00:02:23,430 --> 00:02:24,290
Right, Mentor?

55
00:02:25,480 --> 00:02:27,410
If possible, we'll let you see him.

56
00:02:27,610 --> 00:02:29,070
I'll take you to him later.

57
00:02:30,720 --> 00:02:31,860
Alright. Get in the car now.

58
00:02:31,860 --> 00:02:32,470
Move.

59
00:02:34,750 --> 00:02:35,750
What's your name?

60
00:02:35,960 --> 00:02:36,680
Hu Xiaoyue.

61
00:02:37,280 --> 00:02:38,280
I'm Mai Hongchao,

62
00:02:38,310 --> 00:02:39,240
the eldest senior to you.

63
00:02:39,240 --> 00:02:40,640
Hello, Senior Hongchao.

64
00:03:51,750 --> 00:04:01,760
[The Punishment]

65
00:04:02,040 --> 00:04:03,140
[Punish those who commit crimes
and make mistakes]

66
00:04:03,140 --> 00:04:03,690
[so as to discipline them,]

67
00:04:03,690 --> 00:04:03,960
[and execute those
who violate the prohibitions]

68
00:04:03,960 --> 00:04:04,260
[so as to terrify would-be violators.]

69
00:04:04,260 --> 00:04:05,810
[Guanzi – On Laws and Standards]

70
00:04:06,670 --> 00:04:09,360
[Episode 14]

71
00:05:27,610 --> 00:05:31,010
[Zhang Xin, Chairwoman of Xinrui Holdings]

72
00:05:54,480 --> 00:05:56,310
Did you read the content?

73
00:05:58,909 --> 00:05:59,640
Yes.

74
00:06:00,040 --> 00:06:01,170
You shouldn't have.

75
00:06:02,430 --> 00:06:03,290
For reading it,

76
00:06:03,520 --> 00:06:04,690
now you have to die.

77
00:06:06,360 --> 00:06:08,020
I didn't mean to do so at first.

78
00:06:08,960 --> 00:06:09,890
I was planning to

79
00:06:11,040 --> 00:06:12,300
return it to its owner.

80
00:06:13,930 --> 00:06:14,970
You got any ideas?

81
00:06:15,460 --> 00:06:16,680
We the Longwan people

82
00:06:17,510 --> 00:06:19,440
can definitely outperform Ma Jin.

83
00:06:20,350 --> 00:06:21,550
We're more obedient,

84
00:06:21,640 --> 00:06:22,630
more tactful,

85
00:06:24,260 --> 00:06:25,100
and smarter.

86
00:06:35,120 --> 00:06:37,200
Do you think you could figure out

87
00:06:37,750 --> 00:06:40,950
Ma Jin's getaway route
without my consent to disclose it?

88
00:06:41,680 --> 00:06:42,390
He Biao,

89
00:06:43,390 --> 00:06:45,990
where do you think
your information came from?

90
00:06:49,159 --> 00:06:50,130
I know...

91
00:06:51,750 --> 00:06:53,610
you didn't want Ma Jin to get away.

92
00:06:55,159 --> 00:06:57,090
I made what you hoped for come true.

93
00:06:58,390 --> 00:06:59,750
I truly look forward...

94
00:07:00,510 --> 00:07:01,970
to working with you again.

95
00:07:06,390 --> 00:07:07,950
You're not qualified yet.

96
00:07:09,430 --> 00:07:10,580
For what it's worth,

97
00:07:11,000 --> 00:07:13,160
since you've had that matter done for me,

98
00:07:13,160 --> 00:07:15,320
I'll let you know if I need

99
00:07:15,360 --> 00:07:16,420
your help again.

100
00:07:16,950 --> 00:07:18,750
But if you're hoping for more...

101
00:07:19,560 --> 00:07:21,020
I advise you not to

102
00:07:22,270 --> 00:07:23,800
overestimate yourselves.

103
00:07:44,700 --> 00:07:47,590
[Tianye]

104
00:08:06,010 --> 00:08:08,090
[Tianye]

105
00:08:53,320 --> 00:08:54,400
You're injured?

106
00:08:54,720 --> 00:08:56,720
Come on in. Let me dress your wounds.

107
00:09:00,080 --> 00:09:01,280
I promised you before

108
00:09:02,950 --> 00:09:04,610
that I'd come find you if I won.

109
00:09:06,170 --> 00:09:07,080
I kept my word!

110
00:09:10,780 --> 00:09:12,360
The three things I promised you

111
00:09:12,360 --> 00:09:13,420
will all come true.

112
00:09:45,600 --> 00:09:46,460
The typhoon finally passed.

113
00:09:46,460 --> 00:09:47,630
[One month later]

114
00:09:47,630 --> 00:09:50,150
The long-awaited good weather
has returned to Hanzhou.

115
00:09:50,150 --> 00:09:51,600
Yesterday, Hanzhou Public Security Bureau

116
00:09:51,600 --> 00:09:52,510
announced at a press conference

117
00:09:52,510 --> 00:09:53,150
[Jinding Group]

118
00:09:53,150 --> 00:09:55,200
that a criminal gang that had entrenched
in Hanzhou for 20 years,

119
00:09:55,200 --> 00:09:57,440
featuring illegal gambling, loan sharking,

120
00:09:57,440 --> 00:09:59,270
and extortionate debt recovery,

121
00:09:59,270 --> 00:10:00,150
was finally dismantled.

122
00:10:00,150 --> 00:10:00,720
[Jinding Group]

123
00:10:00,720 --> 00:10:03,080
The key members of this criminal gang
have been arrested

124
00:10:03,080 --> 00:10:04,330
upon approval,

125
00:10:04,390 --> 00:10:06,240
while the ringleader Ma Jin
remains at large.

126
00:10:06,240 --> 00:10:08,440
The police are actively pursuing him.

127
00:10:08,720 --> 00:10:10,790
In the recently issued
Class A wanted notice,

128
00:10:10,790 --> 00:10:13,050
Ma Jin's name is prominently on the list.

129
00:10:53,600 --> 00:10:54,720
Comrade Han Lu,

130
00:10:54,720 --> 00:10:58,050
in the municipal commendation ceremony
held a few days ago,

131
00:10:58,080 --> 00:10:59,480
a first-class merit medal

132
00:10:59,480 --> 00:11:01,280
was awarded to Comrade Wang Tao.

133
00:11:02,300 --> 00:11:05,000
[First-Class Merit Medal]

134
00:11:05,320 --> 00:11:07,920
The provincial department
has also initiated

135
00:11:08,390 --> 00:11:09,520
a donation campaign

136
00:11:09,910 --> 00:11:12,720
for the families
of fallen police officers.

137
00:11:14,270 --> 00:11:15,200
Here is the money

138
00:11:15,910 --> 00:11:17,240
donated by the comrades

139
00:11:17,840 --> 00:11:18,960
in the provincial office

140
00:11:18,960 --> 00:11:20,220
and us in the municipal

141
00:11:21,320 --> 00:11:22,440
Public Security Bureau,

142
00:11:22,440 --> 00:11:23,120
[Archives]

143
00:11:23,120 --> 00:11:25,360
along with the bonus
associated with the honor.

144
00:11:25,360 --> 00:11:26,360
Please accept it.

145
00:11:28,080 --> 00:11:30,340
It's only a small token of appreciation.

146
00:11:31,870 --> 00:11:32,750
Also,

147
00:11:33,720 --> 00:11:35,030
after much effort,

148
00:11:36,120 --> 00:11:38,410
we've found a compatible kidney donor

149
00:11:38,750 --> 00:11:40,010
for Wang Tao's mother.

150
00:11:40,670 --> 00:11:41,490
A transplant

151
00:11:41,750 --> 00:11:43,680
will be arranged in just a few days.

152
00:11:45,870 --> 00:11:46,840
Comrade Han Lu,

153
00:11:47,120 --> 00:11:48,550
if you meet any difficulties
in the future,

154
00:11:48,550 --> 00:11:50,350
feel free to contact us anytime.

155
00:12:17,030 --> 00:12:18,830
Anyway, I don't agree with this.

156
00:12:19,030 --> 00:12:20,360
If you really want to go,

157
00:12:20,360 --> 00:12:20,910
then...

158
00:12:21,160 --> 00:12:22,520
you have to take me with you.

159
00:12:22,520 --> 00:12:23,890
What would you even be doing there?

160
00:12:23,890 --> 00:12:24,910
Didn't you say it yourself?

161
00:12:24,910 --> 00:12:26,360
You're the gas pedal. I'm the brake.

162
00:12:26,360 --> 00:12:29,080
When have brakes and gas pedals
ever been separated?

163
00:12:29,080 --> 00:12:30,610
Look how impulsive you are.

164
00:12:31,080 --> 00:12:31,720
Wait.

165
00:12:31,960 --> 00:12:33,620
Shouldn't we report it first?

166
00:12:34,000 --> 00:12:36,300
Confirm first, then report.

167
00:12:38,840 --> 00:12:39,390
Tao.

168
00:12:41,360 --> 00:12:42,610
We used to say

169
00:12:43,080 --> 00:12:45,270
you were the brake
and I was the gas pedal.

170
00:12:45,270 --> 00:12:47,510
After everything that's happened lately,

171
00:12:47,510 --> 00:12:48,390
from now on,

172
00:12:49,240 --> 00:12:51,620
let me floor that gas pedal.

173
00:13:07,840 --> 00:13:10,880
[Hanzhou Public Security Bureau
Staff Meal Card]

174
00:13:11,080 --> 00:13:11,960
My name's Wang Tao.

175
00:13:11,960 --> 00:13:13,390
We'll be colleagues from now on.

176
00:13:13,390 --> 00:13:14,450
Have you eaten yet?

177
00:13:14,630 --> 00:13:16,630
Let me help you get a meal card first.

178
00:13:17,200 --> 00:13:18,750
Aren't there other things to do
before that?

179
00:13:18,750 --> 00:13:19,340
Trust me,
the meal card is really important.

180
00:13:19,340 --> 00:13:22,750
[Hanzhou Public Security Bureau
Staff Meal Card]

181
00:13:22,750 --> 00:13:23,960
Your meal card looks

182
00:13:24,360 --> 00:13:25,390
as good as new.

183
00:13:26,240 --> 00:13:28,170
You've been using mine for so long.

184
00:13:28,270 --> 00:13:29,120
Now,

185
00:13:29,430 --> 00:13:29,630
[Hanzhou Public Security Bureau
Staff Meal Card]

186
00:13:29,630 --> 00:13:31,030
it's my turn to use yours.

187
00:13:46,910 --> 00:13:47,640
Where's Mai?

188
00:13:47,910 --> 00:13:48,480
He left.

189
00:13:51,720 --> 00:13:52,550
Wang Xu...

190
00:13:52,960 --> 00:13:54,740
had a sudden heart attack a few days ago

191
00:13:54,740 --> 00:13:55,670
and passed away.

192
00:13:56,200 --> 00:13:57,130
I heard about it.

193
00:13:58,890 --> 00:13:59,980
Now that he's gone,

194
00:14:00,750 --> 00:14:03,280
Ma Jin is the only one
who knows the mastermind

195
00:14:04,240 --> 00:14:05,300
behind everything

196
00:14:05,910 --> 00:14:07,580
that Ji Zhujiang mentioned previously.

197
00:14:07,580 --> 00:14:09,830
Ji Zhujiang's confession shows

198
00:14:11,000 --> 00:14:12,850
that there are many people behind Ma Jin.

199
00:14:12,850 --> 00:14:14,070
But Ji Zhujiang

200
00:14:14,240 --> 00:14:16,550
has no idea who these people actually are.

201
00:14:16,550 --> 00:14:17,480
All he knows is

202
00:14:18,360 --> 00:14:20,000
that they only take orders
from one person,

203
00:14:20,000 --> 00:14:20,800
who is usually

204
00:14:21,270 --> 00:14:22,550
referred to as "Boss."

205
00:14:24,270 --> 00:14:25,190
I think

206
00:14:25,340 --> 00:14:27,660
this person is probably related

207
00:14:28,320 --> 00:14:29,750
to the Xu Li case.

208
00:14:33,600 --> 00:14:36,060
They have a strict hierarchy...

209
00:14:36,830 --> 00:14:38,160
What kind of person...

210
00:14:39,090 --> 00:14:40,290
could this "Boss" be?

211
00:14:40,480 --> 00:14:42,080
No matter who this person is,

212
00:14:42,510 --> 00:14:44,000
how powerful and how deeply

213
00:14:44,000 --> 00:14:45,260
concealed he or she is,

214
00:14:46,240 --> 00:14:48,000
we must root this culprit out.

215
00:14:51,790 --> 00:14:52,480
Chu!

216
00:14:52,980 --> 00:14:53,610
Ye.

217
00:14:56,140 --> 00:14:56,780
Ye,

218
00:14:57,390 --> 00:14:58,870
Qin Feng

219
00:14:59,080 --> 00:14:59,880
is quite good.

220
00:15:00,030 --> 00:15:03,400
He made great contributions
to the case about Ma Jin and Luo Bo.

221
00:15:03,400 --> 00:15:04,800
He deserves a promotion,

222
00:15:05,120 --> 00:15:06,030
to deputy chief

223
00:15:06,360 --> 00:15:07,160
or even chief.

224
00:15:07,320 --> 00:15:09,050
He stands a high chance of both.

225
00:15:09,180 --> 00:15:10,910
It depends on his performance.

226
00:15:13,150 --> 00:15:14,210
The case is closed.

227
00:15:14,240 --> 00:15:15,870
Why not go back to the provincial office?

228
00:15:15,870 --> 00:15:16,730
I'm afraid not.

229
00:15:17,270 --> 00:15:18,150
As I told you,

230
00:15:19,200 --> 00:15:21,750
I'm like a falling leave
returning to my roots.

231
00:15:21,750 --> 00:15:23,880
Do you have unfinished business here?

232
00:15:25,320 --> 00:15:26,730
Hu Xiaoyue's death

233
00:15:27,290 --> 00:15:29,420
is attributed to someone

234
00:15:30,150 --> 00:15:31,630
besides Wang Xu and Ma Jin.

235
00:15:32,240 --> 00:15:33,500
Ji Zhujiang confessed

236
00:15:34,300 --> 00:15:36,830
that he and his fellows
worked for one person,

237
00:15:36,870 --> 00:15:38,740
who he had never met.

238
00:15:39,440 --> 00:15:41,030
Despite all that time searching,

239
00:15:41,030 --> 00:15:42,030
we've got no lead.

240
00:15:42,710 --> 00:15:43,590
I believe

241
00:15:44,240 --> 00:15:45,080
this person

242
00:15:45,380 --> 00:15:47,090
is the real mastermind.

243
00:15:49,270 --> 00:15:50,750
Actually, I think it's time

244
00:15:50,750 --> 00:15:52,570
you let your mentees work on it.

245
00:15:52,870 --> 00:15:55,470
Give young people a chance
to gain experience.

246
00:15:55,510 --> 00:15:56,320
You're going to

247
00:15:56,320 --> 00:15:57,320
retire in just a few years.

248
00:15:57,320 --> 00:15:58,780
Why tire yourself out?

249
00:15:58,940 --> 00:16:00,750
Exactly because retirement is approaching,

250
00:16:00,750 --> 00:16:02,560
I'd hate to leave the force with regrets.

251
00:16:02,560 --> 00:16:05,480
I must catch this mastermind,

252
00:16:07,000 --> 00:16:09,700
or I can't face my mentees.

253
00:16:10,750 --> 00:16:11,360
Alright.

254
00:16:12,150 --> 00:16:13,240
If my support

255
00:16:13,240 --> 00:16:15,200
is needed in the line of duty,

256
00:16:15,870 --> 00:16:16,800
just let me know.

257
00:16:17,600 --> 00:16:18,120
Okay.

258
00:16:18,560 --> 00:16:21,690
[Hanzhou Public Security Bureau]

259
00:16:23,440 --> 00:16:24,080
You...

260
00:16:24,600 --> 00:16:25,400
Aren't you...

261
00:16:25,960 --> 00:16:26,760
Aren't you...

262
00:16:27,270 --> 00:16:28,500
Isn't he Mr. Ye?

263
00:16:29,270 --> 00:16:30,800
Let me reintroduce myself.

264
00:16:30,870 --> 00:16:31,720
I am Zeng Xu.

265
00:16:32,080 --> 00:16:33,670
I once carried out an undercover mission

266
00:16:33,670 --> 00:16:34,530
under the alias

267
00:16:34,750 --> 00:16:35,610
of "Ye Siyuan."

268
00:16:35,720 --> 00:16:36,390
Today,

269
00:16:37,000 --> 00:16:38,600
I'm officially reinstated.

270
00:16:42,320 --> 00:16:43,240
I'm Liu Ruyi.

271
00:16:43,720 --> 00:16:44,650
Nice to meet you.

272
00:16:44,960 --> 00:16:45,750
Nice biceps.

273
00:16:45,750 --> 00:16:47,030
Work out with me sometime!

274
00:16:47,030 --> 00:16:48,190
I'm Yang Zhengang.

275
00:16:48,270 --> 00:16:49,550
Pleasure to meet you.

276
00:16:49,550 --> 00:16:51,320
I'd appreciate your help in the future.

277
00:16:51,320 --> 00:16:53,200
I may have to trouble you
to brief me about the team.

278
00:16:53,200 --> 00:16:54,260
-Sure.
-Thank you.

279
00:16:57,790 --> 00:16:58,590
Officer Bian.

280
00:16:59,750 --> 00:17:00,750
How have you been?

281
00:17:05,440 --> 00:17:06,960
What a brilliant strategy by Director Ye!

282
00:17:06,960 --> 00:17:07,790
Wasn't it, Yang?

283
00:17:07,790 --> 00:17:08,680
It surely was.

284
00:17:10,960 --> 00:17:12,960
It was truly visionary and resourceful

285
00:17:12,960 --> 00:17:14,440
of Director Ye to send me

286
00:17:14,790 --> 00:17:16,119
far behind enemy lines.

287
00:17:16,160 --> 00:17:17,589
Of course, I, a highly competent aide, was

288
00:17:17,589 --> 00:17:19,680
also the key to success
as I bravely infiltrated the foes.

289
00:17:19,680 --> 00:17:21,940
I was put through
hardships and torture,

290
00:17:22,130 --> 00:17:23,390
but it doesn't matter,

291
00:17:23,790 --> 00:17:25,319
as all that is behind me now.

292
00:17:25,400 --> 00:17:26,839
I hope to have your help

293
00:17:27,240 --> 00:17:28,750
and support in the future.

294
00:17:28,750 --> 00:17:30,210
Let's work hard together!

295
00:17:30,270 --> 00:17:32,000
-Welcome back!
-Welcome back!

296
00:17:32,640 --> 00:17:33,790
Thank you very much.

297
00:17:33,790 --> 00:17:35,850
I'm not sure about that torture part.

298
00:17:35,880 --> 00:17:38,010
But you certainly chasing a good time.

299
00:17:39,210 --> 00:17:41,270
It's just a small misunderstanding.

300
00:17:42,030 --> 00:17:42,830
Officer Bian!

301
00:17:43,510 --> 00:17:44,420
Officer Bian!

302
00:17:46,240 --> 00:17:47,550
I acted like a party animal

303
00:17:47,550 --> 00:17:50,030
only to disguise my real identity
as an undercover cop.

304
00:17:50,030 --> 00:17:50,640
Oh, right.

305
00:17:52,550 --> 00:17:53,750
I'd like to apologize

306
00:17:55,660 --> 00:17:57,060
for my offensive remarks

307
00:17:57,640 --> 00:17:58,840
last time at karaoke.

308
00:17:59,160 --> 00:18:00,940
I hope you can forgive me.

309
00:18:02,350 --> 00:18:03,110
Really?

310
00:18:04,590 --> 00:18:05,550
You looked like a real thug.

311
00:18:05,550 --> 00:18:07,550
That didn't seem like acting at all.

312
00:18:10,590 --> 00:18:11,160
Wait.

313
00:18:11,640 --> 00:18:12,680
I really wasn't acting...

314
00:18:12,680 --> 00:18:14,740
No, no, I was indeed acting back then!

315
00:18:20,090 --> 00:18:21,420
Something on your mind?

316
00:18:23,680 --> 00:18:24,680
Stop laughing.

317
00:18:25,560 --> 00:18:26,920
Just say it out loud.

318
00:18:33,400 --> 00:18:35,130
Let me think about how to put it.

319
00:18:35,590 --> 00:18:36,480
What is it?

320
00:18:42,000 --> 00:18:42,960
I'm planning...

321
00:18:44,510 --> 00:18:45,370
to get married,

322
00:18:47,070 --> 00:18:48,530
to Ziyi from Zhao Village.

323
00:18:51,030 --> 00:18:51,880
So,

324
00:18:52,720 --> 00:18:54,520
I'm here to ask for your opinion.

325
00:18:55,370 --> 00:18:56,680
My opinion?

326
00:18:58,200 --> 00:19:00,160
Why are you asking for my opinion?

327
00:19:00,970 --> 00:19:04,270
You should talk to Ziyi first, right?

328
00:19:04,650 --> 00:19:06,550
Before your father proposed marriage,

329
00:19:06,550 --> 00:19:08,210
he asked for my opinion first.

330
00:19:09,110 --> 00:19:09,880
Well, Dad asked you,

331
00:19:09,880 --> 00:19:10,790
so I chose to ask you too.

332
00:19:10,790 --> 00:19:11,850
I need your advice.

333
00:19:12,550 --> 00:19:13,840
You silly boy.

334
00:19:16,110 --> 00:19:17,030
Ziyi

335
00:19:17,030 --> 00:19:18,110
is

336
00:19:18,400 --> 00:19:19,680
a really nice girl.

337
00:19:20,200 --> 00:19:22,400
I'm aware of what kind of person she is.

338
00:19:23,330 --> 00:19:24,030
She...

339
00:19:24,510 --> 00:19:25,550
is very tolerant.

340
00:19:26,000 --> 00:19:27,350
But nothing matters more

341
00:19:27,350 --> 00:19:29,010
than what the two of you think.

342
00:19:29,350 --> 00:19:31,210
Have you both thought it through?

343
00:19:31,510 --> 00:19:34,680
Is the affection between the two of you
at its peak right now?

344
00:19:34,680 --> 00:19:36,680
If you're not sure of it,

345
00:19:36,680 --> 00:19:38,080
then you shouldn't rush.

346
00:19:39,720 --> 00:19:40,640
I'm sure of it.

347
00:19:41,720 --> 00:19:44,590
I'd like to start a family
before pursuing career ambitions.

348
00:19:44,590 --> 00:19:46,680
She and I have known each other
since childhood.

349
00:19:46,680 --> 00:19:48,210
We went to school together.

350
00:19:48,240 --> 00:19:49,700
Anyway, I consider her...

351
00:19:50,540 --> 00:19:51,540
my perfect match.

352
00:19:55,640 --> 00:19:56,360
Well,

353
00:19:57,310 --> 00:19:59,290
I can't offer much advice.

354
00:19:59,720 --> 00:20:00,400
However,

355
00:20:01,590 --> 00:20:03,690
I want you to remember one thing.

356
00:20:05,030 --> 00:20:06,960
That is, raising your own small family

357
00:20:06,960 --> 00:20:09,160
and managing the big community of Longwan

358
00:20:09,160 --> 00:20:10,420
are actually the same.

359
00:20:10,920 --> 00:20:13,720
If you are to earn respect and trust

360
00:20:13,790 --> 00:20:15,580
from everyone,

361
00:20:15,720 --> 00:20:17,880
then you must constantly make real efforts

362
00:20:17,880 --> 00:20:19,700
and try convincing others.

363
00:20:20,440 --> 00:20:22,480
When Ziyi marries you,

364
00:20:22,480 --> 00:20:23,440
she'll become

365
00:20:24,200 --> 00:20:25,550
part of our family.

366
00:20:26,480 --> 00:20:27,690
But even so,

367
00:20:27,830 --> 00:20:29,110
her care for you is not

368
00:20:29,830 --> 00:20:31,640
something to take granted for.

369
00:20:32,750 --> 00:20:34,350
You must earn that

370
00:20:34,350 --> 00:20:36,400
by caring for her too.

371
00:20:36,400 --> 00:20:37,720
Do you get it, son?

372
00:20:39,030 --> 00:20:39,860
Son,

373
00:20:41,770 --> 00:20:43,090
life is long.

374
00:20:44,810 --> 00:20:46,830
Make sure you try your best
to build a life with her.

375
00:20:46,830 --> 00:20:48,000
Don't slack off.

376
00:20:51,160 --> 00:20:52,310
I'll keep that in mind.

377
00:20:52,310 --> 00:20:53,640
I will absolutely

378
00:20:54,510 --> 00:20:55,790
do my utmost,

379
00:20:58,270 --> 00:21:00,330
and create a grandchild for you soon.

380
00:21:00,400 --> 00:21:01,740
I'm not eager for one yet.

381
00:21:01,740 --> 00:21:03,070
Don't cause me trouble.

382
00:21:03,220 --> 00:21:04,270
Not eager, huh?

383
00:21:04,570 --> 00:21:06,030
See, you're happy
when I don't cause you trouble.

384
00:21:06,030 --> 00:21:06,750
Look at you,

385
00:21:07,230 --> 00:21:09,630
grinning from ear to ear,
beaming with joy.

386
00:21:10,530 --> 00:21:11,440
Thank you, Mom.

387
00:21:27,180 --> 00:21:29,670
[Grand Opening
of Longwan Logistics Co., Ltd.]

388
00:21:34,870 --> 00:21:37,480
[Longwan Logistics Co., Ltd.]

389
00:21:37,480 --> 00:21:38,400
What do you think, Mom?

390
00:21:38,400 --> 00:21:39,200
Pretty nice, right?

391
00:21:39,200 --> 00:21:40,350
All is well arranged.

392
00:21:40,350 --> 00:21:42,910
You have to make a little speech
on this occasion.

393
00:21:42,910 --> 00:21:44,440
I didn't prepare anything.

394
00:21:44,680 --> 00:21:45,400
Leave it to Tianye.

395
00:21:45,400 --> 00:21:45,880
Mom, you do it.

396
00:21:45,880 --> 00:21:46,510
I can't.

397
00:21:47,270 --> 00:21:48,000
Tianye.

398
00:21:48,480 --> 00:21:49,440
Go address the crowd.

399
00:21:49,440 --> 00:21:50,170
No, you do it.

400
00:21:50,270 --> 00:21:51,130
Just do as I say.

401
00:21:51,830 --> 00:21:52,960
Get on the stage now.

402
00:21:55,320 --> 00:21:56,390
Let's applaud!

403
00:22:01,880 --> 00:22:02,780
Everyone,

404
00:22:03,400 --> 00:22:04,690
fellow villagers,

405
00:22:05,400 --> 00:22:06,000
hello.

406
00:22:07,320 --> 00:22:08,420
Today...

407
00:22:08,680 --> 00:22:09,710
really calls for

408
00:22:09,790 --> 00:22:11,270
a celebration.

409
00:22:12,070 --> 00:22:13,400
It also marks the moment

410
00:22:14,010 --> 00:22:15,480
when Longwan marches towards a new future.

411
00:22:15,480 --> 00:22:16,550
[Grand Opening
of Longwan Logistics Co., Ltd.]

412
00:22:16,550 --> 00:22:18,280
In the past, since we were poor,

413
00:22:18,790 --> 00:22:20,680
we were often disdained

414
00:22:21,480 --> 00:22:22,680
and looked down upon.

415
00:22:23,010 --> 00:22:24,070
But such things

416
00:22:24,920 --> 00:22:26,320
will never happen again.

417
00:22:27,200 --> 00:22:29,550
When our logistics company
rises to prominence,

418
00:22:29,550 --> 00:22:32,410
I will definitely create
a prosperous wealthy life

419
00:22:32,680 --> 00:22:33,960
for all the people

420
00:22:33,960 --> 00:22:35,220
in Longwan and Zhao Village!

421
00:22:35,220 --> 00:22:35,400
[Longwan Logistics Co., Ltd.]

422
00:22:35,400 --> 00:22:36,720
Bravo!

423
00:22:59,720 --> 00:23:01,770
It's been a while since the three of us

424
00:23:01,770 --> 00:23:02,810
had tea like now.

425
00:23:04,680 --> 00:23:05,680
Shall we go

426
00:23:05,680 --> 00:23:07,210
catch fish in the sea later?

427
00:23:07,480 --> 00:23:08,680
Just like the old times,

428
00:23:08,680 --> 00:23:09,920
you two will catch fish in the sea,

429
00:23:09,920 --> 00:23:10,920
while I do the roasting on shore.

430
00:23:10,920 --> 00:23:12,050
Don't you feel cold?

431
00:23:13,430 --> 00:23:14,310
You two go have fun.

432
00:23:14,310 --> 00:23:15,710
I need to get back to work.

433
00:23:16,510 --> 00:23:17,640
Didn't you just start resting?

434
00:23:17,640 --> 00:23:19,350
Can't you have a few more days off?

435
00:23:19,350 --> 00:23:20,440
The case isn't solved yet,

436
00:23:20,440 --> 00:23:21,880
and a criminal is still at large.

437
00:23:21,880 --> 00:23:23,080
How can I take a break?

438
00:23:24,310 --> 00:23:25,880
Could Ma Jin have fled abroad,

439
00:23:25,880 --> 00:23:27,830
given what kind of person he is?

440
00:23:29,510 --> 00:23:30,550
Wherever he has fled,

441
00:23:30,550 --> 00:23:32,470
as long as he hasn't been tracked down,

442
00:23:32,470 --> 00:23:35,830
we'll have to keep working,
and even put in overtime. What can I do?

443
00:23:35,830 --> 00:23:37,110
I don't think you should cling

444
00:23:37,110 --> 00:23:38,040
to Ma Jin's case.

445
00:23:38,160 --> 00:23:39,550
With your level of dedication,

446
00:23:39,550 --> 00:23:40,640
you'll be promoted to director
sooner or later,

447
00:23:40,640 --> 00:23:41,110
right?

448
00:23:41,510 --> 00:23:42,070
That's right!

449
00:23:42,070 --> 00:23:42,790
Thank you in advance then.

450
00:23:42,790 --> 00:23:43,450
No problem.

451
00:23:43,550 --> 00:23:44,480
You surely will.

452
00:23:44,590 --> 00:23:46,880
We've established
our own logistics company now.

453
00:23:46,880 --> 00:23:48,610
A bright future's awaiting us.

454
00:23:50,270 --> 00:23:51,790
I think we'll probably become

455
00:23:51,790 --> 00:23:53,590
the invincible trio of Longwan.

456
00:23:56,880 --> 00:23:57,590
It's not a joke.

457
00:23:57,590 --> 00:23:58,520
Let's make a bet.

458
00:23:59,640 --> 00:24:00,700
-On what?
-Come on.

459
00:24:01,680 --> 00:24:02,340
We'll bet on

460
00:24:02,480 --> 00:24:03,880
the future of Longwan.

461
00:24:07,720 --> 00:24:08,220
[Longwan, Hanzhou City]

462
00:24:13,510 --> 00:24:15,790
The future of Longwan
is held in my hand now.

463
00:24:15,790 --> 00:24:17,510
Let's see if it's the thumb.

464
00:24:18,270 --> 00:24:19,510
It really is.

