579
00:28:15,880 --> 00:28:17,070
This is my boyfriend,

580
00:28:17,070 --> 00:28:17,970
Xu Jiajun.

581
00:28:18,270 --> 00:28:19,440
Boyfriend?

582
00:28:19,440 --> 00:28:20,640
